{"tid":612543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無頭9日？】泰「無頭雞」求生多日 不敵細菌感染死","createTime":"2018-04-01T02:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T09:18:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f24fe8a911fc93ae22bda0f24e8b521de6a01004","tid":612543,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"即時國際  2018-03-31 11:46:36 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n泰國叻丕府一間寺廟早前出現一隻「無頭雞」，雖然整個頭都幾乎消失了，但仍然可以行動自如。「無頭雞」周三被送到一家獸醫醫院診治，但延至周四因細菌感染不治。<br />\n<br />\n負責診治的獸醫哇拉妮表示，「無頭雞」入院時已很虛弱，全身都有很多傷口，頭部傷口最為嚴重，呼吸不暢順及嚴重缺水。當地傳媒報道，牠活了9天，不過她估計牠受傷到死亡，總共只能支撐4天。<br />\n<br />\n「無頭雞」逝世後，愛護動物組織志願人士將牠送到一間佛寺，按照人類葬禮儀式，由四位高僧唸經作法，然後再火化。<br />\n<br />\n當地一間寺廟的僧侶本周初在佛堂發現這隻無頭雞，更嘗試用針筒將流質食物從雞的頸部注射入體內，更指無頭雞吃了很多，求生意志看來極強。翌日他起床時，發現無頭雞仍然生存，於是將「無頭雞」送到獸醫醫院。當時醫生指，這隻無頭雞是一隻雄性鬥雞，估計牠的頭部被利器斬掉或遭狗隻咬去，但因為只是失去了臉部，鼻孔還能呼吸，更剩下一截舌頭可以吞咽。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》/蘋果資料室"},{"pid":"d9233e7fbc64e42d07eb767ccb8764d34667bdb2","tid":612543,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037c315af626d1de3a8b4c9d37ff7392e17d4425","tid":612543,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"極大怨念<br />\n雞靈"},{"pid":"10d36e0521bf2528e2f8e6901a1dad9a2da11d35","tid":612543,"uid":65429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"有無圖"},{"pid":"1efdc20803464d41cb628e32bef734acb279708b","tid":612543,"uid":17275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"Kfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a386ba8c366b07d33732110b01e39cf1e01c65d","tid":612543,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"相反見到班為情所困嘅傻屄因為分咗手就嗌生嗌死真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好想叫佢哋係就快啲死, 佢哋真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201a7bdc7d79fed47a1ac34f263acedb810e7469","tid":612543,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"雞中之覇"},{"pid":"eca325d2e8d7dc40f964a80875e6bc109c5ce86a","tid":612543,"uid":29090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"無頭東宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11851cb13b5de5eff4116a48e78113f5d455773","tid":612543,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7777bee32fce760783d66e19d76c8e58a9c1b254","tid":612543,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/無頭雞麥克\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%84%A1%E9%A0%AD%E9%9B%9E%E9%BA%A5%E5%85%8B&d=5MQD4pzSAkkJjZBrjouuh5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=93a7658f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/無頭雞麥克</a>"},{"pid":"adf082cacec51bdbb7c44c5eeb767f26fbb70db9","tid":612543,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"vsauce講過"},{"pid":"9818ffe7419ce050f4c1839c9154865ac914da0d","tid":612543,"uid":53632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"未入院仲行得走得，入院一日就死Q左"},{"pid":"